        <p><lb n="4"></lb>perumāṉaṭikaḷ mēl <lb n="5"></lb>vallavaraiyaṉ paṭai van <lb break="no" n="6"></lb>tu veṇkuḻikkōṭṭai A <lb break="no" n="7"></lb>ḻitta ñāṉṟu vāṇarai <lb break="no" n="8"></lb>yar māmaṭi tirika Eṉa-t <lb n="9"></lb>ti<unclear>ri</unclear>ntu paṭṭār kaṟkāṭ <lb break="no" n="10"></lb>ṭūr-uṭaiya kaṅkatiyarai <lb break="no" n="11"></lb>yar</p>
